Reviewer Confidential Comments to Editor

Summarize briefly the reasons for your recommendation:

As detailed in my review, I think the CP Optimizer model in section 3.5 should be improved to better take advantage of the existing concepts in order to avoid some dependency to time granularity. I think this could be done quite easily. Otherwise I recommend to accept the paper because of the significant contribution on the new propagators.

